#X text 22 101 Below we use [envgen~] and give it a sustain stage by generating a line with a repeated destination of "1". The attack is then 50 ms \, the sustain stage takes 450 ms and the release is 500 ms long. At the bottom we have the same thing \, now implemented with [vline~]., f 56;
#X text 48 606 These are examples of "one shot" envelope \, with a fixed sustained period. Next we'll see how to control the sustain period with gates., f 55;
